{
  "stem": "24651.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, United States, because I had always heard things about United States-- one of the myths, you know-- [LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--like money grows on trees, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father had a brother in-- in Palestine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was one of the you know, one of the settlers who left in 1935.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was one of the brothers that got away from my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] He was very idealistic and started a kibbutz-- kibbutz Ein HamIfratz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then another uncle who survived, my Uncle Jack, was-- he-- when the war began, he was in Italy studying engineering.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he escaped on a boat to Shanghai.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was taken prisoner of war by the Japanese.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was in a prison during the war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he returned to the United States.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I had an uncle in neither-- in-- in both countries.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we also had some distant cousins in the United States who sponsored us to come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in March-- March 25, 1947, we-- well, first, we went to Paris.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- we-- we were there a couple months.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My father enrolled me in-- in a school to learn English at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then in March 25, 1947, we-- we came on a boat to New York.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- the boat's name was the Marine Falcon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a marine boat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, the women had to be on one floor, and the men were on a-- on another floor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I was separated again from my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I think that--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It took-- it took a long time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it took about 10 days or 8 days, something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a raging storm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and then we came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The two of us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just the two of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
